Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是多洛莫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我等神明手上抢走的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由多种禁忌的技术制成的破坏型兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:00:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再这样下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就能镇压城堡了 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能继续在此地战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即回神界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类已经是苟延残喘之辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不立即撤退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕貝有我们几个他行 先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没救出妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然从战场中央冒出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先去个避人耳目的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 丽塔 你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种不祥的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手 艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跟我们一起逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦罗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的王在那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了人类的王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去会全灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別杀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦罗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只看见他飞得超快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知妮娜被吹到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你成功逃狱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼睛...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩一只也能看见你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此话怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为国王 竟然挑起战争 把城市都毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还跟我跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喊你抱住我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我能变成龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德大人 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别随便碰裸体女士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路过的僵尸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为我会放跑你们？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走丽塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这么关心飞走的爆炸头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神已被击退了 先这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回城堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔依然处于昏迷状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何人类的王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能找到那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个破坏型兵器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个技术出现在米斯塔尔西还没有人神魔的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即旧世界的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便从我等手中夺走了石板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类根本不可能拥有将其拼接起来的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个兵器拥有打破世界的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将世界引向灭亡的为量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像巴哈姆特一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 我没闯祸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多亏了妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 凯撒和师傅被抛下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我去看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？等...太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你陪着圣女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別回王都哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是罪犯加越狱犯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:21:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回王都
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看凯撒和爆炸头过得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜 妮娜交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 丽塔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去神界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的战争 我看见艾尔了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个光芒是艾尔的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽罗妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退的众神应该回神界了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是目前唯一与艾尔有关的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我不知道神界的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:22:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 搞不好有办法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:22:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此话当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得故乡的奶奶说过以前经常去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.89,0:23:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 去妮娜的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.82,0:23:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没有别的线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊 骏鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见识到多洛莫斯的力量了吧 石头的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.64,0:23:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我同步 变成手的形状 biubiubiu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直飒爽得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神击的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回乡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:24:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,biubiubiu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周还要看哦